        public static String[] listNamespaceSort(Wiki wiki,
                                         int ns,
                                         String... pages)
                                  throws IOException
        Returns all the items in an array that are within the specified namespace. e.g. listNamespaceSort(list, WIKI.FILE_NAMESPACE, wiki);
        Parameters:
        wiki - The wiki object to use.
        ns - The namespace filter. Items in this namespace shall be returned.
        pages - The titles (including namespace) to check.
        Returns:
        The list of items in the list that were in the specified namespace.
        Throws:
        IOException - Network error

      • arrayNuke

        public static String[] arrayNuke(String[] list,
                                 String reason,
                                 String talkReason,
                                 Wiki wiki)
        Deletes all the elements in an array and their associated talk pages
        Parameters:
        list - The array to use
        reason - The reason to use while deleting
        talkReason - The reason to use when deleting talk pages of the pages we're deleting. Specify "null" if talk pages are not to be deleted
        wiki - The wiki object to use.
        Returns:
        An array containing the elements we were unable to delete.
